rows.label: bf07510100_0010
rows.name:
You're finally here.
I've been expecting you.

rows.label: bf07510100_0035
rows.name: So you finally gave up your little human act.

rows.label: bf07510100_0040
rows.name:
...Tch, not only can't you find your place,
your thoughts are all over the place too.

rows.label: bf07510100_0070
rows.name:
Hell if I know.
She's probably dead by now.

rows.label: bf07510100_0080
rows.name:
Don't joke around!
I'm still alive!

rows.label: bf07510100_0092
rows.name: Don't make such a scary face.

rows.label: bf07510100_0094
rows.name: I'm just getting back what I lost 500 years ago...

rows.label: bf07510100_0110
rows.name: You're never going to see her again.

rows.label: bf07510100_0120
rows.name:
Heh...
Man, this is really laughable.

rows.label: bf07510100_0140
rows.name: That salvager brat from back then

rows.label: bf07510100_0150
rows.name:
is now standing before me with such 
a confident look on your face.

rows.label: bf07510100_0160
rows.name:
Of course!
As if I could lose to the likes of you!

rows.label: bf07510100_0170
rows.name: ...I'll give you credit for making it this far.

rows.label: bf07510100_0250
rows.name: Metsu's power will destroy anything it touches!

rows.label: bf07510100_0260
rows.name: It'll take your arm or your head right off!

rows.label: bf07510100_0290
rows.name: There's nothing you can do about this, you know.

rows.label: bf07510100_0320
rows.name: I should have used this power earlier.

rows.label: bf07510100_0340
rows.name: That those days might come back again...

rows.label: bf07510100_0350
rows.name: Lives have been lost...because I was afraid...

rows.label: bf07510100_0370
rows.name: But I was told, that I'm free.

rows.label: bf07510100_0380
rows.name: I've realized the meaning of my life.

rows.label: bf07510100_0400
rows.name:
Metsu, your power destorys all matter,
mine regenerates life.

rows.label: bf07510100_0410
rows.name:
As long as the other has the will to live,
I can amplify it.

rows.label: bf07510100_0420
rows.name: I can regenerate any wound in an instant.

rows.label: bf07510100_0430
rows.name: The same goes for Blade weapons.

rows.label: bf07510100_0440
rows.name: They're originally made from our bodies, after all.
